Interface Positionable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CollisionArea, CollisionObject, Sizeable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Circle, CollisionBox, CollisionCircle, CollisionPoint, CollisionPolygon, ConcurrentPointQuadTree, ConcurrentRegionQuadTree, EquilateralTriangle, Point, PointQuadTree, Polygon, Rectangle, RegionQuadTree, RegularHexagon, RegularPentagon, RegularPolygon, Shape, Triangle

    public interface Positionable
    A common interface for objects that can be positioned with an x and y coordinate
